item.title: Ep14 Pubcast, WriteFreely and Plume
item.description: Download Here Music provided by Unfa Follow me across the fediverse! unklebonehead@hzhome.ntroradio.com So I got started on FreeCodeCamp As I mentioned in a blog post last week I want to learn how to code. Mainly so I can understand the topics I am covering here on this podcast and to help me be a better self hoster but I would love to get a new job where I am home a lot more than just 34 hrs a week.
